//:: X0_UD_SURR_9_10
//:: Surrender on having taken 9/10 hit points damage.
//:: OnUserDefinedEvent handler. This REQUIRES uncommenting the 
//:: OnDamaged user defined event in the OnSpawn handler for the NPC. 
